    content: "<strong><a href=\"http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2006/06/060614000759.htm\">Acupuncture Relieves Symptoms Of Fibromyalgia, Mayo Clinic Study Finds</a></strong>\n\nScienceDaily (2006-06-13) -- Fibromyalgia is a disorder considered disabling by many, and is characterized by chronic, widespread musculoskeletal pain and symptoms such as fatigue, joint stiffness and sleep disturbance. No cure is known and available treatments are only partially effective. ... <em>&gt; <a href=\"http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2006/06/060614000759.htm\">read full article</a></em>",
