    title: "🍂 November: A Season of Gratitude, Giving & Self Care",
    excerpt: "As Jacksonville’s breeze cools and the pace of the year begins to settle, November reminds us to slow down, breathe deeply, and reflect on all we’ve been given — and all we have yet to give. At Health…",
